4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program provides 16 weeks of intensive training, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp culminates in an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop